snippet.title: Pool Panic | Beach Day  | Adult Swim Games
snippet.description:
The world's least realistic pool simulator, Pool Panic, releases on Switch and Windows PC via Steam on July 19, 2018. Explore a gorgeous overworld, play 100+ levels, or challenge your friends to a host of weird local multiplayer stages. ON JULY 19, 2018!
 
Website: http://www.poolpanic.com
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/pool-panic-switch
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/522240/Pool_Panic/
